STATE
v.
Angela Deborah LEWIS. No. 558PA04-2. Supreme Court of North Carolina. October 10, 2006. Daniel P. O'Brien, Assistant Attorney General, C. Colon Willoughby, Jr., District Attorney, for State of NC.
